canonical:
  title: 偶題
  author: 柳方善
  language: lzh
  text: 結茅仍補屋種竹故爲籬多少山中味年年獨自知
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 偶題
  author: 柳方善
  language: lzh
  text: 結茅仍補屋。種竹故爲籬。多少山中味。年年獨自知。
korean:
  title: 우제
  author: 유방선
  language: kor
  text: |-
    띠풀을 엮어 지붕을 깁고
    대를 심어 울타리로 삼네
    과히 없지 않은 산중에 사는 맛을
    해마다 혼자서 깨쳐 가네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0620&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: A Casual Poem
  author: Yu Bang-seon
  language: eng
  text: |-
    I thatch the roof with woven reeds,
    Plant bamboo for my garden fence.
    The mountain's subtle flavors—
    Year after year, I taste them alone.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The poem captures the solitary joy of rural retreat, where the speaker finds meaning in humble tasks and intimate communion with nature.
